data.title: Dell Equallogic PS400E Series, Used Dell servers, build your own server
data.meta_description: All used Dell EqualLogic PS400E Series server, refurbished Dell server for sell, Dell EqualLogic PS4000E Series of virtualized iSCSI SAN arrays.
data.text:
Base Model: Single controller with 2GB5 battery-backed memory High Availability Model: Dual controllers with a total of 4GB battery-backed memory Battery-backed memory provides up to 72 hours of data protection. Hard Disk Drives: Eight or sixteen SATA hot-pluggable hard disk drives Drive Capacities: 7,200 RPM SATA II drives available in 250GB , 500GB or 1TB System Capacities 2TB using eight 250GB SATA disk drives

4TB using sixteen 250GB SATA disk drives

8TB using sixteen 500GB SATA disk drives

16TB using sixteen 1TB SATA disk drives RAID Support: Automatic RAID 5, RAID 6, RAID 10, and RAID 50 Volumes: Up to 256 Snapshots: 128 per volume / up to 2,048 total TCP Network Support: IPv4, IPv6 core support Security: CHAP authentication

Access control for iSCSI

Access control for management interfaces including RADIUS support Expansion Option: Can be combined with other EqualLogic PS Series arrays in the same SAN group online. A maximum of two (2) PS4000 arrays can be in a group.
